 Beitrag für Wachstum und Strukturwandel der italienischen Volkswirtschaft differenziert analysiert. Die weitverbreiteten Negativurteile hinsichtlich der mangelnden Steuerungseffizienz der italienischen Industriepolitik werden durch die Ergebnisse dieser Studie relativiert.  aThe study addresses the relationship between industrial policy and economic development between 1943/45 and 1975 in Italy. For the first time, based on extensive source materials and archival data collections, the study traces the planning and implementation of government subsidies for industry and analyzes their differential impact on growth and structural change in the Italian economy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aItalien. 4aWiederaufbau. 4aWirtschaftspolitik. 7aHISTORY / Social History.2bisacsh  aItaly.  aReconstruction.  aeconomic policy.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831106842780 cprintz978311068416240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311068422340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110684223423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110684223.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020